{"tid":711093,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"<長文慎入>嚟緊訂畢業袍嘅大家一定要小心呢間shop!!","createTime":"2018-06-21T09:23:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-16T05:15:19.000Z","uid":70573,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"34c6d9653317b73b7e464fc58369df9a624b235d","tid":711093,"uid":70573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T09:23:20.000Z","msg":"無諗過連登開第一個post竟然係同大家分享啲咁唔愉快嘅體驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> sorry篇分享有啲長 唔得閒睇嘅請小心Goxx Rexxxxxxxx 以下簡稱GR<br />\n<br />\n話說呢排畢業季 五月初朋友A問起不如大家一齊夾份喺Goxx Rexxxxxxon訂畢業袍 因為見優惠多啲咁就一齊訂 <br />\n<br />\nTotal係8個人訂 我frd嗰邊有5個人 我呢邊訂自己 家姐同一個朋友嘅 7件都係學士袍 家姐嗰件係訂碩士袍 而落單就係由朋友A直接同間shop直接聯繫 <br />\n<br />\n以下係我同朋友A對話 佢係5月4號叫大家入數 留意番嗰陣要入碩士袍嘅價錢係540<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/21/160008_f8a59d36b3047855c14856305adb7de1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F21%2F160008_f8a59d36b3047855c14856305adb7de1.png&h=01115792&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係同朋友A訂之前其實我有問一問間shop大概訂5套嘅價錢 時間係4月28號 嗰陣GR話學士加碩士袍一齊訂會有優惠 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">碩士袍價錢係500 而到貨時間係2-3星期</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/21/163621_c6c9f8926dde38bd7458db3897438875.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F21%2F163621_c6c9f8926dde38bd7458db3897438875.png&h=9de02595&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/21/163622_48f4a4212ac36439ceb9ca8201bfaf10.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F21%2F163622_48f4a4212ac36439ceb9ca8201bfaf10.png&h=222bc784&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後我cap番圖比朋友A問番呢件事 A話我知GR話加咗價 其實只係幾日間嘅事就突然加價我都覺得無言 不過諗住反正都要訂就大家一齊訂埋 咁GR之後都有同番朋友A講話碩士袍要一個月先拎得 即係6月7號前點都會收到 因為家姐其實都好想趁6月尾去畢業旅行嗰陣帶袍影 諗住6月頭收到都仲有時間走盞<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/21/164942_0c7215fe0b8bc1657f4e1835019cf9ca.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F21%2F164942_0c7215fe0b8bc1657f4e1835019cf9ca.png&h=57b943ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後都以為好順利 因為大概2個幾星期就收到朋友A通知話學士袍已經到貨 咁我地都拎咗所有學士袍<br />\n<br />\n但點知到今個月7號 同家姐傾起先醒起件碩士袍未拎 咁我唔想煩到A就直接拎咗GR電話問<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/21/170645_b4dd556ff343e7329a6e1b4fa3bdfff3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F21%2F170645_b4dd556ff343e7329a6e1b4fa3bdfff3.png&h=30e4c6c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/21/170646_fedf1c7626e339a69c87a8b02d7e57c2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F21%2F170646_fedf1c7626e339a69c87a8b02d7e57c2.png&h=658a520f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/21/170647_9997c65b351a8463a1c270395e3147b1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F21%2F170647_9997c65b351a8463a1c270395e3147b1.png&h=31fabf78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實GR一直係拖字訣 而且態度被動同唔老實 如果唔係一直追問我諗多數筆錢係追唔番 而錢都算事小 作為一間咁大嘅shop竟然零誠信 唔問得緊啲都唔知原來件碩士袍係一直都唔存在 甚至連道歉都無就咁退錢就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n依家已經要到飛嘅時間家姐根本嚟唔切搵第二間訂 所以今次分享真係好想話比大家知搵類似shop之前記得小心啲 問清楚曬先好落訂 同埋發覺有咩唔妥記得問緊啲間shop退錢方案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ee91c26a100405c9415905b4f2d72b7c090a9ae","tid":711093,"uid":131622,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T05:15:19.000Z","msg":"呢間好耐之前已經勁多劣評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}